  "title": "Full-Time Sales Associate (Basic + Commission)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>We are looking for Full-Time Sales Associate!</strong></em><br /><em><strong>Join us if you have passion in Home Fragrances & Customer Service or love interacting with customers!</strong></em><br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Interact with customers to sell products and provide customer service</li><li>Product knowledge and recommendations based on customer preferences and needs</li><li>Weekly stock replenishment/stock take</li><li>Maintain housekeeping standards in store/counters</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Team Player</li><li>Able to work with minimal supervision</li><li>Drive to achieve individual sales target on monthly basis, in a team environment</li><li>Prior experience in Retail Industry will be an added advantage</li><li>5 days work week (Including Weekends & PH)</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong><br />Shift : Retail hours<br />Location : Metro / Takashimaya (Rotational)<br />Remuneration : Basic Salary + **<strong>Attractive</strong>** Commission <u><em>(From $2,300 + Commission)</em></u><br />Attire : All Black Smart Casual Outfits<br />Training will be provided</p><p><em>To know more of our products, please visit us at: https://stefaniparfumerie.com/</em></p><p><br /><em>Interested candidates, click apply!</em></p>",
