    "description": "<p>Innova Distribution was born in 2013, Singapore, with capital injection from Swiss investors with strong credentials in the beauty and fragrance industry. Innova is a fast growing distribution company specialising in luxury home fragrances. Several years on, the company now represents leading luxurious brands from Australia and Europe.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Innova has grown its expertise in marketing and distribution of home fragrances and evolved as a trusted supplier to reputable retailers and leading departmental stores regionally. Today, Innova Distribution has extended its wings into Malaysia.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Innova prides itself to distribute products of premium quality to enhance the well-being and health of individuals through scenting. At Innova Distribution, the company embraces and is passionate about fragrances.</p>",
